et/images/images/bac-si-tieu-phau.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Adam Health Care', 'Experience the Art of Caring', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '9-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-04-14 15:31:33', '2018-04-14 08:31:33', '', 9, 'http://news.aigiupminhkhong.vn/2018/04/14/9-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
